    <title>0.3.0</title>
    <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 07:56:54 +0000</pubDate>
    <sparkle:version>23</sparkle:version>
    <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
    <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
    <description><![CDATA[<h2><a href="https://github.com/chenasraf/OpenUpdater/compare/v0.2.0...v0.3.0">0.3.0</a> (2026-06-22)</h2>
<h3>Features</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>ui:</strong> move ignore list and unsupported apps into the main window (<a href="https://github.com/chenasraf/OpenUpdater/commit/978d25098be31bb0a643d4d16c2f697f9a2711af">978d250</a>)</li>
<li><strong>updates:</strong> add Stop button to halt the update queue (<a href="https://github.com/chenasraf/OpenUpdater/commit/6ca26f205bb1bb2ff1cbfa73c4f2cc67a829b342">6ca26f2</a>)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Bug Fixes</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>installer:</strong> accept long DMG license agreements (PAGER=cat) (<a href="https://github.com/chenasraf/OpenUpdater/commit/2dc820da527eddb0e05f1c0ab9f30ec98fd6ec42">2dc820d</a>)</li>
<li><strong>installer:</strong> keep source extension so pkg installs work (<a href="https://github.com/chenasraf/OpenUpdater/commit/961a6a98d016ef5be4abd949de97a4b3b72ce37f">961a6a9</a>)</li>
<li><strong>recipe:</strong> Firefox (<code class="notranslate">org.mozilla.firefox</code>) (<a href="https://github.com/chenasraf/OpenUpdater/commit/08e02c674771b4e23595e76ba68f2a2fd8b63b82">08e02c6</a>)</li>
<li><strong>recipe:</strong> Google Chrome (<code class="notranslate">com.google.Chrome</code>) (<a href="https://github.com/chenasraf/OpenUpdater/commit/aedb59e8338eb0345ecf660198c29e6513e8e817">aedb59e</a>)</li>
<li><strong>recipe:</strong> Visual Studio Code (<code class="notranslate">com.microsoft.VSCode</code>) (<a href="https://github.com/chenasraf/OpenUpdater/commit/49f19f53b0b1fe71a69fcb61631bc0578499d940">49f19f5</a>)</li>
</ul>]]></description>
